snippet.title: The Forever Labyrinth | Official Trailer
snippet.description:
There is a Labyrinth at the end of the time. Will you escape?

The Forever Labyrinth is a replayable narrative adventure made in collaboration with Google Arts & Culture. Explore the halls and uncover its secrets, but beware: in every Labyrinth, there is a monster...

Play now at http://goo.gle/foreverlabyrinth
